{"tid":811532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"filecoin兩年八倍回報 80/90後最後逃生門?","createTime":"2018-09-09T02:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T15:03:19.000Z","uid":129225,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71f5ed3c5cf005a510a285350b409da4bb4b1a25","tid":811532,"uid":129225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:03:04.000Z","msg":"【蘋聞追click】2,000萬買機 掘未上市虛擬貨幣 投資者得米定得弊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180909/58655977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180909%2F58655977&d=Zdays%2Fva7Gj8FXNPFS381TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d60b996b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180909%2F58655977&h=43fbfad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180909/58655977</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>自稱「幣少爺」的黃鉦傑，今年初開設facebook專頁，介紹區塊鏈技術及投資虛擬貨幣心得。他其後轉為推銷建基於IPFS（InterPlanetary File System，星際檔案系統）的虛擬貨幣filecoin，主打礦機買賣及託管合約，初期<span style=\"color: red;\">每部礦機售港幣25,000元，後加至27,500元，據稱已賣出約800部，推算涉款最少2,000萬元</span>；投資者可選擇將礦機託管，每部機兩年託管費15,000元。全部款項須在簽訂合約後30日內全數支付。<br />\n<br />\n根據黃鉦傑描述，IPFS為「可改變網絡生態」的點對點儲存技術，只要提供閒置硬碟容量供他人使用，即可獲得filecoin作為獎勵。他指IPFS礦機主要消耗品是硬碟，耗電量僅為傳統礦機十分之一，加上香港網速世界有數，希望募集投資者在filecoin上市前建立香港第一的礦池，增加挖掘filecoin的機會，「賺取第一批暴利」，<span style=\"color: red;\">又指投資者可三個月回本，兩年可賺取八倍回報</span>。</blockquote><br />\n好似吹到好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇玩開虛擬貨幣巴打解答吓"},{"pid":"bbbfa72507f0e231817951a22e237328bf98c715","tid":811532,"uid":108467,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:04:20.000Z","msg":"傻仔，依加仲玩虛擬貨幣，根本就係現代版龐式騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c7787bb5736ed150f78cf354fe0af73d15ae21","tid":811532,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:05:17.000Z","msg":"有得賺就唔會咁高調啦，on9！"},{"pid":"60f10388eca3a0d51ea9f4e5e325f98e28ee2f3e","tid":811532,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:07:51.000Z","msg":"好心正正經經儲錢買樓啦"},{"pid":"b86a5c84d3e4f880e8e1c93c8ebd2dc92ceef74c","tid":811532,"uid":208074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:08:19.000Z","msg":"仲咁多傻仔信"},{"pid":"bd2333f55b84919629035569fbb9a9e9cd4d22cf","tid":811532,"uid":149582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:03:19.000Z","msg":"等佢上市買黎渣住都好 個概念係革命性既"}]}